{"tid":589062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話就話選民，其實由此至終都冇得選","createTime":"2018-03-11T15:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T16:07:37.000Z","uid":91471,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06427aee19a8642130a848f9d049cec1e1e0e3ac","tid":589062,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"好掛住有天琦參選嗰陣，雖然唔係新東選民，<br />\n但起碼都感覺到我地係可以選一個代表到自己嘅人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家望住嗰堆參選嘅，根本冇一個投得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n短短兩年，成個氣氛已經唔同哂，<br />\n就好似本來嗰一絲曙光，捉唔住消失左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b0f372e61a90df9248e45ccbfd8be035ca9317","tid":589062,"uid":91471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"好灰"}]}